FBIS3-9918 "drlat039_k_94005" FBIS-LAT-94-039 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Feb 1994 SOUTH AMERICA Argentina UN Notified of Offer To Clear Falklands Mines PY2402181894 Buenos Aires Radio Nacional Network in Spanish 1600 GMT 24 Feb 94 PY2402181894 Buenos Aires Radio Nacional Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] The Argentine Republic has officially notified the United Nations that it advised the United Kingdom that it is willing to help clear the Malvinas Islands' territory and waters of mines laid during the 1982 war. To that effect Argentina submitted maps locating approximately 30,000 mines.
